content.raw: I wrote e-mail yesterday to “[subt-help@googlegroups.com](mailto:subt-help@googlegroups.com)” asking for output of crashed \(not started\) instances. Note, that I use the same docker for all worlds, with different robot names, and it is based on “subt\_seed” example. This morning I noticed **TerminatingInstances Error: AdminReview** = what is this?!
